749
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:12,250
That's strange.

750
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:13,430
I'll make a call.

751
00:31:16,820 --> 00:31:17,480
Captain Qi!

752
00:31:25,780 --> 00:31:26,150
Stop!

753
00:31:29,190 --> 00:31:30,120
