When I make money in the future,

833
00:34:41,739 --> 00:34:43,139
I'll pay you back double.

834
00:34:46,699 --> 00:34:47,360
Officer Qi,

835
00:34:48,790 --> 00:34:49,989
I've already told you

836
00:34:50,540 --> 00:34:52,580
everything I know.

837
00:34:53,500 --> 00:34:55,760
What more do you want to squeeze out of me?

838
00:34:58,590 --> 00:34:59,920
When pus gathers inside,

839
00:34:59,920 --> 00:35:01,720
it's bound to burst eventually.

840
00:35:01,950 --> 00:35:02,830
You carry around

841
00:35:02,830 --> 00:35:03,420
so many

842
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:05,030
dirty secrets every day.

843
00:35:06,090 --> 00:35:07,090
Aren't you tired?

844
00:35:08,700 --> 00:35:10,220
Do you know Liu Shusheng?

845
00:35:14,350 --> 00:35:16,550
No, never heard of him. I don't know him.

846
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:19,770
You're afraid of Liu Shusheng too?

847
00:35:19,770 --> 00:35:20,700
I don't even know him.

848
00:35:20,700 --> 00:35:22,230
How could I be afraid of him?

849
00:35:23,270 --> 00:35:23,790
No,

850
00:35:23,790 --> 00:35:26,100
I can see you're very afraid.

851
00:35:26,100 --> 00:35:27,060
I don't know him.

852
00:35:27,080 --> 00:35:27,950
Please, don't ask anymore.

853
00:35:27,950 --> 00:35:29,210
I don't know anything.

854
00:35:29,290 --> 00:35:31,440
He must know everything about you.

855
00:35:32,520 --> 00:35:34,850
You're afraid he'll go after your family.

856
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:48,600
No, I don't know him.

857
00:35:49,270 --> 00:35:50,200
Why are you crying?

858
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:52,500
Can't I miss my wife and children?

859
00:35:55,680 --> 00:35:57,570
[Qinchuan City Detention Center]

860
00:35:57,570 --> 00:35:58,310
Captain Yang.

861
00:35:58,310 --> 00:35:59,110
What's wrong?

862
00:35:59,410 --> 00:36:00,720
Come with me to Shan's house.

863
00:36:00,720 --> 00:36:01,250
Let's go.

864
00:36:21,670 --> 00:36:22,470
What's wrong?

865
00:36:23,930 --> 00:36:25,890
This police car and uniforms

866
00:36:26,570 --> 00:36:28,970
make us too obvious going into the village.

867
00:36:30,180 --> 00:36:30,990
That's right.

868
00:36:32,020 --> 00:36:33,280
Shan's been arrested.

869
00:36:33,850 --> 00:36:35,910
How will his wife and children get by?

870
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:39,400
There are plain clothes in the trunk.

871
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:40,400
Let's get changed

872
00:36:40,610 --> 00:36:41,380
and take a taxi there.

873
00:36:41,380 --> 00:36:41,910
Alright.

874
00:37:13,990 --> 00:37:14,580
Who is it?

875
00:37:15,470 --> 00:37:17,070
This is Shan's house, right?

876
00:37:18,500 --> 00:37:18,990
Yes.

877
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:23,090
We're here to investigate
and gather some information.

878
00:37:24,430 --> 00:37:25,360
Shan isn't home.

879
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:26,970
Please open the door first.

880
00:37:28,970 --> 00:37:29,700
Police.

881
00:37:31,760 --> 00:37:32,240
Open up.

882
00:37:47,250 --> 00:37:48,120
What

883
00:37:48,940 --> 00:37:49,870
brings you here?

884
00:37:50,330 --> 00:37:51,530
We're here to see you.

885
00:37:51,640 --> 00:37:53,900
Any difficulties in your life recently?

886
00:37:54,050 --> 00:37:54,580
No.

887
00:37:55,410 --> 00:37:56,290
Nothing at all.

888
00:37:56,890 --> 00:37:57,740
Everything's fine.

889
00:37:57,740 --> 00:37:58,800
How about the kids?

890
00:37:58,820 --> 00:37:59,820
They're not here?

891
00:38:00,640 --> 00:38:02,040
The older one isn't home.

892
00:38:02,270 --> 00:38:03,310
The little one hasn't been

893
00:38:03,310 --> 00:38:04,710
feeling well these days.

894
00:38:05,270 --> 00:38:06,290
He's sleeping now.

895
00:38:06,290 --> 00:38:07,550
What's wrong with him?

896
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:09,160
He's got a runny nose.

897
00:38:09,310 --> 00:38:10,920
He probably caught a bit of a cold.

898
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:12,380
What happened to his face?

899
00:38:16,620 --> 00:38:18,290
What happened? How did he get hurt so badly?

900
00:38:18,290 --> 00:38:19,300
It was dark at night.

901
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:20,530
He fell off his bike.

902
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:23,350
Fell off a bike and got hurt this badly?

903
00:38:23,530 --> 00:38:25,390
Someone beat him up, didn't they?

904
00:38:25,620 --> 00:38:26,310
Who did it?

905
00:38:26,620 --> 00:38:28,120
He is usually very well-behaved.

906
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:29,290
He doesn't cause trouble either.

907
00:38:29,290 --> 00:38:30,710
How could he get into a fight with someone?

908
00:38:30,710 --> 00:38:32,020
He just fell, that's all.

909
00:38:32,020 --> 00:38:33,220
Has someone been

910
00:38:34,010 --> 00:38:34,920
intimidating you lately?

911
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:36,380
No one is intimidating us.

912
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:39,140
I'm just an honest farmer
trying to make a living from the land.

913
00:38:39,140 --> 00:38:40,270
I don't know anyone.

914
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:43,330
Really, no one is intimidating us.

915
00:38:46,450 --> 00:38:47,310
Tell me,

916
00:38:47,790 --> 00:38:48,450
who hit you?

917
00:38:49,230 --> 00:38:50,160
Don't be afraid.

918
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:59,700
You mustn't hide anything, okay?

919
00:39:01,600 --> 00:39:02,860
I'm telling the truth.

920
00:39:03,790 --> 00:39:04,500
Take this.

921
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:06,780
What... What is this for?

922
00:39:06,780 --> 00:39:08,580
It's for treating his injuries.

923
00:39:08,980 --> 00:39:09,910
My phone number.

924
00:39:10,470 --> 00:39:11,020
Keep it.

925
00:39:12,250 --> 00:39:14,250
If anyone intimidates you again,

926
00:39:14,270 --> 00:39:15,180
give me a call.

927
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,180
Hey little one,

928
00:39:18,070 --> 00:39:18,880
call me.

929
00:39:19,210 --> 00:39:20,140
You must tell us.

930
00:39:20,260 --> 00:39:22,590
If anything happens, you must let us know.

931
00:39:26,220 --> 00:39:27,020
Liu Shusheng.

932
00:39:28,070 --> 00:39:29,270
He beat me to it again.

933
00:39:29,550 --> 00:39:32,350
I'll drag him out, skin and all.

934
00:39:32,990 --> 00:39:34,120
Don't be so anxious.

935
00:39:34,390 --> 00:39:36,590
We need to take things one step at a time.

936
00:39:38,070 --> 00:39:38,500
What?

937
00:39:41,140 --> 00:39:41,750
Did you...

938
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:44,550
leave us any money?

939
00:39:53,200 --> 00:39:53,600
You...

940
00:39:54,220 --> 00:39:54,890
You don't have money?

941
00:39:54,890 --> 00:39:55,350
My...

942
00:39:56,150 --> 00:39:57,880
My wallet is in my police uniform.

943
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,410
I left my uniform in the car.

944
00:39:59,690 --> 00:40:00,690
How do we get back?

945
00:40:00,820 --> 00:40:01,820
How do we get back?

946
00:40:02,770 --> 00:40:03,500
Let's go back

947
00:40:04,240 --> 00:40:05,640
and borrow some from her.

948
00:40:05,910 --> 00:40:07,350
Twenty yuan.

949
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:10,550
I just gave her money,
but now you want to borrow from her?

950
00:40:10,550 --> 00:40:11,060
Or else?

951
00:40:11,660 --> 00:40:12,660
What should we do?

952
00:40:14,990 --> 00:40:15,660
Dacang,

953
00:40:16,180 --> 00:40:18,310
you should start eating some walnuts.

954
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:20,640
It might help that slow brain of yours

955
00:40:20,790 --> 00:40:21,580
catch up.

956
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,420
How about 150 yuan?

957
00:40:24,510 --> 00:40:25,600
I haven't eaten yet.

958
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:26,800
Let's eat some paomo.

959
00:40:36,450 --> 00:40:36,910
What?

960
00:40:41,650 --> 00:40:42,310
Lamb paomo.

961
00:40:42,640 --> 00:40:43,570
Do you want some?

962
00:41:18,640 --> 00:41:20,040
What are you looking for?

963
00:41:20,890 --> 00:41:22,370
Where's my shirt?

964
00:41:22,730 --> 00:41:24,590
There's a celebration tomorrow.

965
00:41:24,600 --> 00:41:26,000
I need to dress formally.

966
00:41:28,980 --> 00:41:29,910
It's right here.

967
00:41:31,080 --> 00:41:32,280
Can you iron it for me?

968
00:41:33,990 --> 00:41:34,990
Stop right there.

969
00:41:35,300 --> 00:41:36,100
What's wrong?

970
00:41:37,970 --> 00:41:38,630
Take it out.

971
00:41:39,370 --> 00:41:40,170
Take what out?

972
00:41:40,220 --> 00:41:41,390
Take it out,

973
00:41:42,080 --> 00:41:43,620
and I'll pretend none of this ever happened.

974
00:41:43,620 --> 00:41:45,380
What nonsense are you talking about?

975
00:41:45,380 --> 00:41:46,440
What are you doing?

976
00:41:46,810 --> 00:41:47,770
I told you.

977
00:41:48,210 --> 00:41:49,740
You think I didn't see that?

978
00:41:50,120 --> 00:41:51,690
Why won't you listen to me?

979
00:41:51,940 --> 00:41:52,670
What is this?

980
00:41:53,630 --> 00:41:55,010
I'm asking you, what is this?

981
00:41:55,010 --> 00:41:56,540
What are you yelling about?

982
00:41:56,560 --> 00:41:58,490
I paid for this out of my own pocket.

983
00:41:59,300 --> 00:42:00,470
Since you've already seen it,

984
00:42:00,470 --> 00:42:01,870
I might as well be honest.

985
00:42:02,340 --> 00:42:03,430
I've got some debts.

986
00:42:03,430 --> 00:42:04,130
They said

987
00:42:04,150 --> 00:42:06,370
if I can't pay up, they'll come
cause trouble at home.

988
00:42:06,370 --> 00:42:07,230
I'm not scared.

989
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:09,770
But your father is someone important.

990
00:42:09,850 --> 00:42:11,380
When the time comes,
it'll be his reputation on the line.

991
00:42:11,380 --> 00:42:12,420
What are you saying?

992
00:42:12,420 --> 00:42:13,560
Why are you bringing up my father?

993
00:42:13,560 --> 00:42:15,220
-What are you talking about?
-Give it to me!

994
00:42:15,220 --> 00:42:16,310
Let go!

995
00:42:16,330 --> 00:42:17,310
-Give it to me.
-You're snatching it,

996
00:42:17,310 --> 00:42:18,020
yet you think...

997
00:42:18,020 --> 00:42:19,310
-You think you're right?
-Give it to me.

998
00:42:19,310 --> 00:42:21,210
What do you want? You want to hit me?

999
00:42:21,210 --> 00:42:22,240
What do you want to do?

1000
00:42:22,240 --> 00:42:24,350
Can't you understand what I'm saying?

1001
00:42:24,350 --> 00:42:25,500
You want to hit me, don't you?

1002
00:42:25,500 --> 00:42:26,120
-Give it to me.
-Right?

1003
00:42:26,120 --> 00:42:27,990
Don't get involved in
other couples' business.

1004
00:42:27,990 --> 00:42:29,300
You'll only bring trouble upon yourself.

1005
00:42:29,300 --> 00:42:30,940
Ouch! Let go!

1006
00:42:32,500 --> 00:42:32,950
It hurts!

1007
00:42:32,950 --> 00:42:33,970
You want to hit me, don't you?

1008
00:42:33,970 --> 00:42:35,160
Help!

1009
00:42:35,390 --> 00:42:36,870
-Help!
-Come on.

1010
00:42:36,990 --> 00:42:37,830
Hurry!

1011
00:42:38,830 --> 00:42:39,840
How dare you hit me!

1012
00:42:39,840 --> 00:42:40,900
How dare you hit me!

1013
00:42:40,910 --> 00:42:41,470
How dare you hit me!

1014
00:42:41,470 --> 00:42:42,220
Alright.

1015
00:42:42,270 --> 00:42:42,870
Calm down.

1016
00:42:43,100 --> 00:42:43,500
Let go!

1017
00:42:43,870 --> 00:42:44,530
Let go of me!

1018
00:42:44,620 --> 00:42:45,660
I'll take you on.

1019
00:42:45,870 --> 00:42:46,700
That's enough.

1020
00:42:46,700 --> 00:42:47,830
Come on, Mr. Lu.

1021
00:42:47,830 --> 00:42:49,310
-I won't give in anymore!
-Let him go.

1022
00:42:49,310 --> 00:42:49,910
Let him go.

1023
00:42:50,390 --> 00:42:51,160
Come on, hit me.

1024
00:42:51,160 --> 00:42:52,420
-Come on.
-Look at her.

1025
00:42:53,060 --> 00:42:53,950
Lai, you bastard.

1026
00:42:53,950 --> 00:42:55,120
What do you think you're doing?

1027
00:42:55,120 --> 00:42:56,310
Why are you putting on airs?

1028
00:42:56,310 --> 00:42:58,060
Come on. If you've got the guts, try me.

1029
00:42:58,060 --> 00:42:59,580
If you dare to lay a finger
on Xiaoman today,

1030
00:42:59,580 --> 00:43:00,660
I'll rip your arm off.
